   Technology &amp; Health:
   Fuji Team Makes
   Artificial `Eye'
   Using a Protein
   ----
   By Jerry E. Bishop
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/17/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<CO>
